{"tid":1497322,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本防衛省擬在完成F-35B部署前  讓美軍先用出雲號","createTime":"2019-08-23T02:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T05:53:47.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"480eef5b17e834048a4547e55b47574ce74b1220","tid":1497322,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T02:14:05.000Z","msg":"日本政府將進行最大級、出雲級護衛艦的航艦化改裝。防衛大臣岩屋毅今日表示，日本自衛隊從來沒有護衛艦搭配戰鬥機運用的經驗，今後將尋求美方協助。自衛隊與美軍的合作將更一步強化。<br />\n<br />\n日本政府去年修訂防衛計畫大綱，將進行出雲級護衛艦假版的耐熱性改裝，讓出雲級護衛級甲板可以承受戰機起降，今後將搭配可垂直起降的美國最新銳匿蹤戰機F-35B運用。<br />\n<br />\n共同社報導，日本防衛省有意在自衛隊完成F-35B部署之前，讓駐日美軍的F-35B先在出雲級護衛艦上使用，亦及，讓美軍使用出雲級護衛艦。據相關人士稱，美軍先行利用的想定包括美軍F-35B參與美日聯合軍演時在艦艇上起降。此外，飛行中因機體故障緊急降落在艦艇等情況也包含在內。<br />\n<br />\n防衛大臣岩屋毅表示，今後與美國將有各種的聯合訓練，證實有做相關的思考。他表示，日本的船艦沒有與F-35B搭配運用的經驗，需要美方的合作和支持分享相關資訊，例如，協助進行檢查和測試。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6811/4004406\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6811%2F4004406&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1aEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=94e51d1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6811/4004406</a>"},{"pid":"3d5d7650db18993d13b167023dd16531e6f5489f","tid":1497322,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T02:21:10.000Z","msg":"亞太都多一隻USS WASP同功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ebdb1dd6f0bb0faae37bdb22b1ca9076377dde","tid":1497322,"uid":53676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T02:22:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0babbe1381b02f5f36de105756e1fb6f41d83e4","tid":1497322,"uid":34804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T02:23:51.000Z","msg":"中國外交部就要強烈不滿啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"195a0b4bde515e55a3df56db7046c7879bb99d56","tid":1497322,"uid":128014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T02:26:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">阿爽！起身返工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"b5855f796f223df409c7dc6ee3bdd924031cef95","tid":1497322,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T05:53:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}